No, Liz.

35:35.000 --> 35:37.868
That's why I was going
to call you.

35:37.870 --> 35:39.102
Carter's not here.

35:39.104 --> 35:39.703
Is she in the cell?

35:39.705 --> 35:43.507
I just went down there
to tell her the good news.

35:43.509 --> 35:45.041
She's gone.

35:45.043 --> 35:47.711
Kyle, where is she?

35:52.550 --> 35:53.116
Crash came by.

35:53.118 --> 35:56.186
Some idiot clerk allowed him
to post bail for her.

35:56.188 --> 35:58.088
No, that's impossible.
She's a minor.

35:58.090 --> 35:59.322
They can't.
I know.

35:59.324 --> 36:01.791
But they did.
When was this?

36:01.793 --> 36:05.929
I don't know.
Maybe any hour ago.

36:05.931 --> 36:06.997
Elizabeth, I'm sorry.

36:06.999 --> 36:08.398
You let her go with him?

36:08.400 --> 36:09.199
She left with him?

36:09.201 --> 36:11.968
It wasn't me--
How could you do that?

36:11.970 --> 36:17.007
I just got her back.
And now she's gone?

36:21.078 --> 36:24.114
She's gone.

