at Bird's.

36:38.296 --> 36:41.598
Wow, dad's book.

36:41.600 --> 36:43.466
Any good?

36:43.468 --> 36:45.168
I wasn't crazy about it, no.

36:45.170 --> 36:46.703
Oh, well.

36:49.340 --> 36:53.610
Who's gonna want to read a book
